                        <div  data-lazy="1" class="module_column tb-column col-full tb_b03i675 first">
                    <!-- module text -->
<div  class="module module-text tb_ba6r197   " data-lazy="1">
        <div  class="tb_text_wrap">
        <p>Houston Cinema Arts Society offers a wide variety of screenings and related programming throughout the year, including a Texas Film Spotlight, Encore Screenings of our CineSpace Short Film Finalists, and advanced access to members-only screenings of premiere feature films. Many of these screenings are free for HCAS Members. Click <a href="https://www.cinemahtx.org/get-involved/membership/">here</a> to learn more about our Membership. </p>
<p>To see lists of our previous screenings <a href="https://letterboxd.com/cinemahtx/lists/">check out our Letterboxd</a>.</p>    </div>
</div>
<!-- /module text -->        </div>
                        </div>
        </div>
